  "title": "A Lesson in Sith Brutality",
  "summary": "In the interrogation chambers of the Star Destroyer Inquisitor, Darth Malign confronts the chained crime lord Tyy'sun Eson and his slicer Jingle, accusing the Maffi Family of overreaching in Imperial space and crossing his agent Axel Vichten over a soured ship deal on Corellia. Eson defends the Family's honor and service, but Malign -- soon joined by the masked Grand Inquisitor Korolov -- means to teach a lesson in Sith brutality, handing Axel a cleaver and inviting him to exact revenge. Eson and Axel trade bitter words about honor, the Force, and the price of dealing with the Sith, while Jingle desperately bargains the codes to the disputed ship to save his own digits. Axel, sickened but committed, ultimately settles on taking both of Eson's thumbs -- one dedicated to the traitor Malif -- as the defiant Twi'lek flicks his own blood at his tormentor and sings a promise of vengeance. Jingle finally surrenders the passcode, and Axel presses a vibro-knife to the slicer's cheek with threats of worse should the code prove false.",
